long_description: the italian job is a london based interior design studio established in 2012, bringing top quality furniture and accessories, encompassing the style of italian design. the italian job supplies an extensive range of high quality furniture, including kitchen cabinets, wardrobes, sofas, bedroom, living room rigorously made in italy. the client, such as the interior designer, architect or building developer, can reflect the own personal style by choosing from a great variety of models and finishes. furniture can also be custom made and fitted on location. on site surveys, interior design consulting, 3d planning, delivery and installation are some of the services provided. working from photographs, ideas, drawings or just sketches, their specialists are happy to design a space just for you. the italian job is also able to accommodate projects from the commercial sector supplying seating solutions to both office and hotel projects.
